fileimporter-desc: Tana dikera faali duma zɛ'ɛta zi'isi sisesi naana la
tag-fileimporter-description: A malum iŋɛ la 'log' sooleŋo n pa'asɛ pooren dɔla la ba n dikɛ ze'ele wiki ayima puan na la
tag-fileimporter-imported-description: Te'ele bisɛ sɛla n ze'ele wiki ayima puan na
fileimporter-mediawiki-api-notfound: A feele mɛ ti a nyɛ 'mediawiki' API ze'ele SourceUrl.
fileimporter-api-badinfo: Foopɔ'ɔsega bii ate'ele bisɛ lasebaarɛ la lebe la API.
fileimporter-api-failedtogetinfo: A feele mɛ ti a lebeyese faali la lasebaarɛ ze'ele: $1
fileimporter-api-nopagesreturned: Pɛga ka boi malum lebe 'remote' API la puan.
fileimporter-api-toomanyrevisions: Ate'ele bisɛ duma la so'e mɛ malum lebe API la puan, kan ta'am yakɛ na.
fileimporter-api-failedtofindapi: A feele mɛ ti a nyɛ API zi'an la ze'ele: $1. $2 $3
fileimporter-cantimporturl: Kan nyaŋɛ dikɛ URL bu'a la yakɛ na
fileimporter-cantimportmissingfile: Kan nyaŋɛ dikɛ faali n borege yakɛ na.
fileimporter-cantimportfileinvalid: Faali wa (or an older revision of this file) tari la yɛla n kan ta'am sakɛ yɛsera la gu'a zuo: $1
fileimporter-warningabusefilter: An. [//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikimedia:Edit_filter automated filter] te'ele baŋɛ la 'potentially unconstructive' demesego ti la dɛna a te'ele bisɛ faali tuusum la puan. Ayıla bii zo'e zo'e te'ele bisɛ ta'am ta'asɛ bala mɛ; ayıla woo pa'alɛ mɛ tilum la iŋɛ n toŋɛ sɛla. Di'e ta'asɛ le ya'asa ti la zagesɛ sɛla woo n wam wa'am na de tukɛ nɛŋa tari yakɛ na.
fileimporter-badnamespace: Malum bisɛ tuure yu'urɛ fole bu'a.
fileimporter-badtoken: Fu 'session' la ka le tuna. N beleni mɛ malum pɔsɛ tari yakɛ na.
fileimporter-badimporthash: 'Import hash' la ka tɔ. N beleni mɛ malum pɔsɛ tari yakɛ na.
fileimporter-filenameerror-default: Yele yoo n boi fu filename la puan.
fileimporter-filenameerror-toolong: Faali la yu'urɛ ti fu tiregera ti fu dikɛ yakɛ na la ba'am wɔgɛ mɛ.
fileimporter-filenameerror-notallowed: Fu tiregeri ti fu tarı la faali n tari yɔ'ɔ $1 yakɛ na. Faali n tari yɔ'ɔ dina wa ka tari yɔ'ɔ wiki wa puan. Sɛla n tari yɔ'ɔ de la: $2.
fileimporter-filenameerror-automaticchan: Faali la yu'urɛ kɔ'ɔm tee la dimɛŋa ze'ele "$1" dɛna "$2"
fileimporter-filenameerror-nosourceexten: Faali la n ze'ele zi'an la ka tari 'extension'.
fileimporter-filenameerror-noplannedexte: Faali sɛka n maasum yu'urɛ la ka tari 'extension'
fileimporter-filenameerror-missmatchexte: 'Target' faali 'extension' la ka tɔ di 'extension' la n boi di 'original' faali la puan la.
fileimporter-duplicatefilesdetected: Faali la ti fu tiregera ti fu dikɛ yakɛ na la pugum bɔna wiki wa puan mɛ.
fileimporter-textrevisions: $1/$2 pɛgerɛ {{PLURAL:$2|revision|revisions}} na tarı loŋɛ ze'ele amalum iŋɛ tuusum la puan.
fileimporter-filerevisions: $1/$2 faali {{PLURAL:$2| version|versions}} na tarı loŋɛ na.
fileimporter-previewnote:
Iŋa de faali la n yakɛ na la ate'ele bisɛ. 
N beleni mɛ bisɛ pɛgerɛ la nima nima dee nyaŋɛ dikɛ yakera.
fileimporter-cleanup-text: Fu ta'am yele n boi wiki la n ze'ele zi'an na la yeti faali n yakɛ na {{SITENAME}}. Ŋwana ta'am iŋɛ fu san pa'asɛ {{$1}} 'template ti the original' faali pɛgerɛ la n boi fu yu'urɛ puan.
fileimporter-cleanup-checkboxlabel: Daalɛ wiki faali duma sɔ'a la ti fu tarı loŋɛ {{SITENAME}} na la
fileimporter-cleanup-failed: Wiki la n ze'ele zi'an mɛŋa demesego la ka tani dɛmesa.
fileimporter-delete-text:
Fu tari yɔ'ɔ ti fu duuse faali la n boi wiki la n ze'ele zi'an na la. 
Fu san bɔta ti faali n yakɛ na duuse faali n boi fu yu'urɛ puan. Loe yɔ'ɔ dina wa:
fileimporter-delete-checkboxlabel: Duuse faali n boi wiki zi'an bɔna fu yu'urɛ puan basɛ.
fileimporter-delete-failed: Faali wa ka ta'am duuse dimɛŋa basɛ n boi $1. N beleni mɛ malum lebe [$2 the original fole] de duuse ka 'manually.
fileimporter-filemissinginrevision: Kan ta'am tari faali yakɛ na se'ere zuo n sɔi la, a te'ele bisɛ la ayima n borege foote faali la puan.
